<style>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=optional");

  :root {
    --newsprint: #f2ede4;
    --ink: #1a1714;
    --red: #c8102e;
    --ink-muted: rgba(26,23,20,0.55);
    --ink-faint: rgba(26,23,20,0.12);
    --ink-rule: rgba(26,23,20,0.18);
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--newsprint);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.55;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

  .layout { max-width: 1060px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; }

  /* Masthead rule */
  .masthead-stripe {
    height: 10px;
    background: var(--ink);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--red);
  }

  /* Topbar */
  .topbar {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 1rem 0 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--ink);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .topbar .brand {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.6rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .topbar .edition {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted); text-align: right; line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Breadcrumb */
  .crumb {
    padding: 0.45rem 0;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
  }
  .crumb a:hover { color: var(--red); }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    padding: 2.75rem 0 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--ink);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) { .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .hero-left .kicker {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red); font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .hero-left h1 {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5.5vw, 3.8rem);
    font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .hero-left .dek {
    font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.4rem;
    background: var(--red); color: #fff;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif; font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    border: 2px solid var(--red);
    transition: background 0.12s, color 0.12s;
  }
  .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--ink); border-color: var(--ink); }

  .hero-shot-wrap {
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 var(--ink);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-shot-cap {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.7rem;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    background: var(--ink); color: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .hero-shot {
    display: block; aspect-ratio: 16/9; overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--newsprint);
  }
  .hero-shot img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

  /* Section rule */
  .section-rule {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 0 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .section-rule .rule-label {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted); font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .section-rule .rule-line {
    flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--ink-rule);
  }
  .section-rule .rule-count {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--red); font-weight: 700;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  /* Apps gallery */
  .apps {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 5px 5px 0 var(--ink);
    background: var(--newsprint);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .app {
    padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr 300px;
    gap: 2rem; align-items: start;
    transition: background 0.12s;
  }
  .app:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  @media (max-width: 800px) { .app { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; } }
  .app:hover { background: rgba(26,23,20,0.03); }

  .app .num-cell { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .app .num {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-weight: 900; font-size: 2.8rem; line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--ink-faint);
  }
  .app--live .num { color: var(--red); }
  .app .status {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.5rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 6px; border: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
    color: var(--ink-muted); text-align: center;
  }
  .app--live .status { background: var(--ink); color: #fff; border-color: var(--ink); }

  .app .body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .app .body .title {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .app .body .tagline {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; font-style: italic;
  }
  .app .body .desc { font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--ink-muted); }

  .app .right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .app .shot {
    display: block; aspect-ratio: 16/9; overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--ink); background: rgba(26,23,20,0.05);
  }
  .app .shot img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .app .shot-placeholder {
    padding: 1rem; height: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-muted); text-align: center;
  }
  .app .ctas { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); border: 2px solid var(--ink); overflow: hidden; }
  .app .ctas--single { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .btn {
    text-align: center; padding: 0.55rem 0.5rem;
    background: transparent; border-right: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink); cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.12s;
  }
  .btn:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--red); color: #fff; }
  .prompt-link {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--ink-muted); text-decoration: underline;
  }
  .prompt-link:hover { color: var(--red); }
  .fork-note {
    font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--ink-muted); line-height: 1.5;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--red); padding-left: 0.6rem; margin-top: 0.3rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* Epilogue */
  .epilogue {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-top: 3px double var(--ink);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .epilogue { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; } }
  .epilogue-col h2 {
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
  }
  .epilogue-col p { font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--ink-muted); }
  .epilogue-col p + p { margin-top: 0.75rem; }
  .epilogue-col .hl { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    padding: 1.25rem 0; font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink-muted);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-rule);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--red); }
</style>

<div class="masthead-stripe"></div>
<div class="layout">
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">Vibes DIY</a>
    <div class="edition">
      For Garage Sales &middot; Five Tools<br/>
      No group chat required
    </div>
  </header>

  <nav class="crumb">
    <a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Garage Sale
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      {{#with apps.[0]}}
      <span class="kicker">Spotlight &mdash; App 01</span>
      <h1>One link. Everyone's in. No group chat needed.</h1>
      <p class="dek">
        The Coordinator handles neighbor sign-ups, spot claims, and the who-needs-change list &mdash; so you can spend Saturday selling, not texting.
      </p>
      <a class="hero-cta" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/og/garage-sale-coordinator">Start the Sign-Up &rarr;</a>
      {{/with}}
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      {{#with apps.[0]}}
      <div class="hero-shot-wrap">
        <div class="hero-shot-cap">The Coordinator &mdash; Live</div>
        <a class="hero-shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="The Coordinator screenshot">
          <img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="garage-sale-coordinator" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"/>
        </a>
      </div>
      {{/with}}
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="section-rule">
    <span class="rule-label">Also in this issue</span>
    <span class="rule-line"></span>
    <span class="rule-count">4 more tools</span>
  </div>

  <section class="apps">
    {{#each apps}}
    {{#unless @first}}
    <article class="app {{#if live}}app--live{{else}}app--pending{{/if}}">
      <div class="num-cell">
        <div class="num">{{num}}</div>
        <div class="status">{{#if live}}Live{{else}}Soon{{/if}}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
        <p class="tagline">{{tagline}}</p>
        <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="right">
        {{#if live}}
          <a class="shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{title}} screenshot"><img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"/></a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Join</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Clone</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix</a>
          </div>
          <a class="prompt-link" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">// start fresh from this prompt</a>
          {{#if fork}}<p class="fork-note">{{fork}}</p>{{/if}}
        {{else}}
          <div class="shot"><div class="shot-placeholder">generating</div></div>
          <div class="ctas ctas--single">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">Start From Prompt</a>
          </div>
          {{#if fork}}<p class="fork-note">{{fork}}</p>{{/if}}
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </article>
    {{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
  </section>

  <div class="epilogue">
    <div class="epilogue-col">
      <h2>The situation</h2>
      <p>
        Every neighborhood sale runs on one person fielding forty texts. Who's setting up where. Who needs change. Who's bringing the card table. Who's out by noon. The Coordinator is <span class="hl">one link, shared in the group chat once</span> &mdash; neighbors sign themselves up, claim their spot, and flag what they need.
      </p>
      <p>
        The other four handle what comes after: making your individual sale findable, tracking shared gear, rating the finds, and splitting the money at the end of the day without a spreadsheet argument.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="epilogue-col">
      <h2>Make it yours</h2>
      <p>
        These five were built for a standard neighborhood multi-family sale. Your situation is probably different &mdash; a church rummage, an estate clearout, a flea market stall, a community room booking. <span class="hl">Clone whichever is closest</span> and describe what's different about your setup.
      </p>
      <p>
        Each app is yours to customize: change the fields, the categories, the split logic, the address prompt. You own the fork. No one else's sale lives in it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{> newsletter}}
  <footer>
    <span>Vibes.diy &middot; <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">homepage</a> &middot; <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/discord">discord</a></span>
    <span>Garage Sale</span>
  </footer>
</div>
